btg.text:
Welcome to Butter Engine!! An engine powered by SOGL 3 graphics!
If you have questions, I will answer them.
This engine should be simple enough. More features will be added later on.
If you decide to use this engine, please credit me by leaving this link in the credits

https://scratch.mit.edu/projects/1071343741/

The engine should be self explanatory, the engine sprite is the one you edit for making games, if there are features you don't see in this engine, please explain what feature to add and what it can do in the comments.
This engine supports plugins as drag and drop, and should have stuff inside the plugins to explain how to implement it.
Shaders are also drag and drop, you can drop shaders into the project and set the engine to use it, if it's compatible.
